A campus-exclusive social app for ULAB students, synced with URMS for verified profiles, class schedules, and course groups. Key features: auto-matched free rooms using real-time schedule data, live location sharing (friends only), club join/leave access, emergency alert system with live location, official event announcements (admins only), complaint box to faculty, chat for friends and coursemates, and secure campus entry via QR + face recognition. UI: clean, card-based, with bottom navigation and modular dashboard. Focus on privacy, trust, utility, and student engagement. Style: youthful, minimal, ULAB-themed. Designed to solve real campus problems through smart connectivity.
